RingofInvocation5060.name: Ring of Invocation #5060
description: When adorned, the ring puts the bearer in a state of astral
projection, revealing ancient ethereal secrets to them. When
celestial bodies align, the user is granted the ability to
communicate with deceased rulers of great fallen
civilizations.

AmuletofInfluence6320.name: Amulet of Influence #6320
description: Long ago in the Dark Ages, a great Grand Wizard forged the
Amulet of Influence through perilous times. Passed through
generations of high sorcerers, this amulet is said to be
imbued with magical properties that grant its wearer the
ability to harness and repurpose the life essence of nearby
entities. As its egg-like center spins, all nearby lifeforms
are influenced to carry out the bearerâ€™s bidding.

CupOfConfusionAndIntellect3788.name: Cup of Confusion and Intellect #3788
description: One sip from the cup will bring the user untold knowledge and
the ability to understand the great mysteries of the world's
past, present, and future... if they are worthy.
